Question: A fuzzy gray baby penguin is near adult penguins in at least one image, and two standing penguins bend their necks and beaks downward toward each other in one image.

Reference Answer: False

Left image URL: http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2007/04_02/05penguinDM_468x743.jpg

Right image URL: http://www.photovolcanica.com/PenguinSpecies/King/ANT09_1399s.jpg

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is there a fuzzy gray baby penguin near adult penguins?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there a fuzzy gray baby penguin near adult penguins?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many standing penguins are bending their necks and beaks downward towards each other?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many standing penguins are bending their necks and beaks downward towards each other?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER2} == 2')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3} == 2')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} xor {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
